item.title: I Would (Not)
item.description: There’s things I’ve said I’d not want, or never do, or never be, and saw such things as negative, and nonetheless I’ve ended up wanting, doing, or becoming many of them. ‘I’d never study at ____ , such an shallow place’ ‘I’d never stop talking with ____ , it means a lot to me’ ‘I’d never put ____ before ____ , its a matter of principles’ ‘I’d never want to learn about ____ , or stuff related to it’
